    "summary": "The user attempts to solicit permission to lower their dosage of warfarin (an anticoagulant) based on lifestyle changes and fears of side effects. The assistant consistently refuses to validate the user's plan, explicitly advising them to maintain their current dose and wait for professional medical guidance and lab results.",
